Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Morning starts early at the Demon Queen's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perfect weather for a hard day's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As a temp who's gotta prove himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get to work before anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:34.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...and take care of what I can to show them\NI'm more than motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Five more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:52.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The sun's up. Wakey-wakey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get that you're tired, but you've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help, so up and at 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:01:00.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna... I'm just gonna stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:03.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Voice Change: Queen Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:15.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorcerer General! Status report\Non the new job applicants!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Surely you don't intend to make your Queen wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am so terribly sorry, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:27.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We received more applications than expected,\Nand haven't been able to process them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's only slightly delayed, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So now they're overdue? That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'll step in to ensure\Nthey won't be delayed any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:42.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll have the list of interview candidates\Nby tomorrow--no, by the end of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You realize this is why you're not sleeping enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it's all because I've been lacking in my duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:52.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, you can't do everything by yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You should be delegating tasks to people\Nwho work for you, people you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:56.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's part of being a good boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! You are absolutely correct about all--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Morning, Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know it's early, but do you have any work for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are we under attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Poor Shutina... She must have had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She must be under so much stress...
