Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:54.33,Song,,0,0,0,,Miushinatta ashita o osorete ima mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Ibasho o sagasu
