Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:01.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:06.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can NOT believe you! Totally unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:07.83,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Hey, why're you mumbling and\Ngrumbling to yourself over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's got you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You! Who else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:16.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every! Infinitesimal! Speck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of your existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon Army was suffering\Nfrom a dire lack of personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:29.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After my highly-destructive assault on their army,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,most of the top brass had returned to\Nthe Demon World to recover from their injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The work they'd left behind had to be handled\Nby those who remained: the Four Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:47.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And nobody knew how to do that work--\Nno one, save for Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the sort of thing that plagues big companies:\Nwork veterans can handle easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:58.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but those veterans don't have time to write\Na manual or train other people to do those tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you have Queen Echidna, who wants\Nto refortify her army as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And someone just can't help\Nbut overwork themselves to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even if it means overworking herself to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That explains why her Icicle Lance barely packs a punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I came here to help with your workload, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could be a little nicer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:29.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why in the world would I be nice to a man\Nwho barges into my room while I'm sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're a succubus, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is your current task list?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, with the highest-priority tasks at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Evaluate applications, reorganize sorcerer corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:06:00.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,regular maintenance on Queen Echidna's\Nretainer homunculi, operating cost reduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's like, fifty tasks on here.\NWhy don't you delegate some of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To whom?! I don't have any colleagues or subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The last task on this list is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Replenishing the mana reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me think here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A number of castle facilities and instruments\Ntapped into mana from the reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Only the person who created them\Ncan replenish them with mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So any reactors that Shutina created could\Nonly be replenished by Shutina herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:40.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If anyone with a different mana wavelength tried\Nto help, the reactor would be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that smirk for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From today on, I'm gonna handle\Nreplenishing your mana reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, that's wonderful.\NThat task is quite the headache to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're not going to ask how I'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:07:00.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're going to mimic my wavelength\Nwith Harmonize, right? It's common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's only common sense to sorcerers\Nas powerful as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, how many reactors are yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not many, considering there are over\Na hundred throughout the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They only have to be replenished once every few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Give me thirty minutes and two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes and two hours and I'll have it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I could get it done in less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll promise you this, and stake my honor as a Hero on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:33.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Promise me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I promise to never, ever disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In two and a half hours, you'll be all like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Oh yay, my workload is gonna be sooo light!\NYou're amazing, Leo! I love you so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you'll jump up and give me a huge kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, go get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been fourteen seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Metamorphose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, I gotta think up a name. Something super cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, one favor, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:16.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you give me the title "Assistant to the Generals"?\NThat'll get people to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How's the name Godhart sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get a move on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...and that's why I've come to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you notice Shutina acting off at all,\Nlet me know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be of help to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't. Shutina would stress out more if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right. Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've returned, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd change up my speaking\Nstyle to blend in better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's only been thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have a little faith. I took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should give you another task, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, not yet. I'm kinda tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've adjusted\Nmy mana wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mirage Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to watch you work while I take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't get in your way. I'll sit here quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got another task for you when\Nyou're done resting, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, you must be rested by now. I need you to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not yet. I need to rest just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've used Metamorphose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This stuff's pretty bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should see about improving the food around here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:50.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been an hour! Surely you're more than rested!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, I need a little more. My mana's still recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You lazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get up this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How are you this heavy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Most sorcerers don't realize you can\Nuse Gravity Root to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:07.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've got enough mana to waste on silly spells,\Nbut you still need to 'recover'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Decisions, decisions... Do I go with\NLord Godhart or Lord Bloodsword?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, I could go with something totally different:\NBlack Knight Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that, Shutina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I understand full well now, Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:31.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're a worthless, lazy leech of time and resources!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And after calmly and coolly thinking this over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've come to the calm conclusion that\Nyou will not be of use to our army in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dio Neel Zod, spiral of radiant light...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fill my hands with your piercing rays of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop! You're going to destroy all your paperwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gae Assail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Demon Queen's legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have to, for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:14.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if I want to join, I'll need to show results\Nand get the Generals on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This, right here, is step one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:26.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dianette, yes? Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By the look of you, all must have gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord Godhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:34.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, call me Black Knight Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From now on-- no, FORSOOTH? Henceforth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Black Knight Onyx, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:41.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, Lord Onyx...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:45.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right then, proceed with your report\Non the reactor maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:54.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The talisman you granted me\Nworked without incident, Lord Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It appears to be durable enough to--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What talisman? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Le-- Lord Onyx, was it not you\Nwho replenished the reactors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:09.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, let her finish her report, Sorcerer General.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The talisman appears to be\Ndurable enough for continued use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:24.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so with your permission, I would like us to continue\Nreplenishing the reactors in your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Would that be allowed, General Shutina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But those are reactors that I created.\NYou'll be able to replenish them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,First, let me explain what exactly I was doing\Nin those thirty minutes I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:50.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I went to the castle workshop and procured\Nan amethyst from the goblin goldsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I filled the amethyst with mana tuned to your wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:14:01.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Amethysts are sturdy stones.\NThey'll stay attuned to a wavelength indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyone who holds it on their person\Nwill be attuned to your wavelength as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I created a talisman with the stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,which only took fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I left the workshop, then lost five minutes\Nto an unexpected distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I took five minutes to find Dianette here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With my last five minutes, I showed her how\Nto use the talisman to replenish the reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:37.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He told me as long as I'm wearing this talisman,\NI can replenish all of your reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After that, I said:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:47.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Find a few other people with the\Nappropriate ability and split the job up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:47.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I found three other sorcerers of similar capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We passed the talisman around to refill the reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I trust, then, that all four of you\Nunderstand the procedure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Sorcerer General is a busy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Form a team of four and assume responsibility\Nfor replenishing her reactors henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll have enough talismans for all of\Nyou within the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:13.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You took a bit longer than I'd like for this task,\Nbut it IS your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I expect you to perform it more quickly come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course, milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the mana reactors\Nhave been replenished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to lessen the burden on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dianette, here, was worried for your health as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, m-my apologies, but yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:52.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know you've been grappling with a mountain\Nof tasks in recent days, General Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,M-might I be of some assistance, General Shutina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:12.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. You focus on your own tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:18.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had neither the courage nor ability to press the matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:25.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But thanks to Lord Onyx, we'll be able\Nto assist with the mana reactors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:30.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If there's anything else we can help with,\Nplease don't hesitate to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:38.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to reach out to you if there\Nare tasks you can help with, Dianette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:39.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good work. You are dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,T'would seem you finally understand\Nmy true labors, Sorcerer General.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All you need to do now is let them handle it\Nand hear their reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll only have to help out if something goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you, I only needed two and a half hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and now your workload is permanently decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Work isn't something that should be done alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Especially not in a large organization where\Nthere are plenty of people who can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Instead of having one extremely-skilled\Nperson work extremely hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,it's best to delegate many\Nsmall tasks out to less skilled people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how you should get most of the work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In an ideal world, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you explain that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could have told me you asked Dianette to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because you worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I'd told you, you would've rushed off\Nto "go check on her".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Most of the people in the army are people you\Ninterviewed, people you trust to perform well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So trust in your judgment,\Nand in the people working beneath you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Run the organization so it could still function\Nif you dropped dead tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of talk for someone\Nwho insisted on working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of life experience under my belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:22.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You make a big show of 'teaching'\Nand 'delegating' to a subordinate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and while they were hard at work,\Nyou did nothing but loaf about in my office!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You slacker! What's your excuse for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You wound me. I was loafing, yes,\Nbut I was also working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:40.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot about from watching you\Nand your cleavage work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I spotted some inefficiencies here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:47.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I took the liberty of rearranging\Nyour priorities. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you say CLEAVAGE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See those seven tasks I circled in red?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can delegate those.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But can they handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Teach them HOW to handle it.\NThat's your job as their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this a map of the Largo Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The fish from that area are fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We could make some scrumptious meals\Nif we got some delivered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:27.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but considering how dangerous\Nthe shipping route would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sorcerer General Shutina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I apologize. I've gravely misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now. I just did my job is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That only makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Despite how harshly I acted\Ntowards you during the interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you still pressed on and did an excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:54.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't well call myself one of the Four Generals\Nif I didn't thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you go down, the whole army goes down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then I REALLY won't have a place to go anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:09.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was just looking out for myself.\NNo need to thank me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And here I was giving you a heartfelt apology!\NHow is anyone supposed to like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I was traveling alone for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:22.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right, better start on my next task.\NCall me if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to working with you, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said after you gave me this task?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I promised I wouldn't disappoint you,\Nthen I said something after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In two and a half hours, you'll be all like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:51.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Oh yay, my workload is gonna be sooo light!\NYou're amazing, Leo! I love you so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you'll jump up and give me a huge kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, go get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll take one on the lips, or on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We could even climb into the bed and-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That hurt WAY more than this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:26.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me to call you if I needed you, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be calling me so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily is headed to Largo on a logistics mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The castle's food and equipment stores are running low,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so we need to make sure this shipment comes in safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that could be a serious issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's not the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:56.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's the mission plan Lily submitted to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:00.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gonna have a big happy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For real?
